The words module
================

    >>> from pysyte import words

This module handles some english words

    >>> expected = [
    ...     ('punch', 'punches'),
    ...     ('fish', 'fish'),
    ...     ('lunch', 'lunches'),
    ...     ('bass', 'basses'),
    ...     ('fax', 'faxes'),
    ...     ('coach', 'coaches'),
    ...     ('rash', 'rashes'),
